data.description: This mid-century gem is the perfect blend of luxury and practicality! Nestled on a generous 1-acre lot in the City of Chillicothe, this 4000 sq ft home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 baths—perfect for those who love hosting. A finished basement with a bar, a great room with a wet bar, and a dedicated hot tub room off the deck ensure seamless entertainment. At its heart, a grand two-story fireplace graces the great room, with large windows bathing the space in natural light. Indulge in the master en suite with its attached dressing room, and appreciate the first-floor laundry for added convenience. The property offers a 2-car attached garage, a detached 2-car garage, a raised garden bed, and a fenced back yard, perfect for privacy and green thumbs alike. Tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this open-concept home invites you to experience tranquility and comfort.
